<div class="jumbotron">
    <div class="row">
        <p class="about">Welcome to the Research Dashboard. The Research Dashboard is a web-based system that allows Researchers, Principal Investigators, Department Heads, Associate Deans for Research and other appropriate personnel access to financial information such as budget, expenditures, encumbrances and budget available in a real-time, easy to navigate and understand format.  The Research Dashboard is user friendly and compatible with Mobile devices.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
        <p class="about">Most pages of the Research Dashboard can be exported into Microsoft Excel for ad-hoc reporting and management of the projects.  Data is organized by Banner Fund Code/Grant with further drill-downs available by fund, account and transactional detail including personnel information. </p>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
        <p class="contact">Questions concerning a particular budget, expenditure or encumbrance should be brought to your department’s administrator or feel free to contract your Contract & Grant Accountant, listing available at <a href="https://www.uah.edu/c-g/contact" target="_blank">https://www.uah.edu/c-g/contact</a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
        <p class="contact">If a Principal Investigator or PI has a question related to Research Dashboard, please also contact <a href="https://www.uah.edu/c-g/contact" target="_blank">UAH Contract and Grant Office</a></p>
    </div>
</div>
